    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain and rinse your <strong>black beans</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>sweet potato </strong>to a baking tray (or two!) with the<strong> chopped</strong> <strong>red pepper</strong>,<strong> cherry tomatoes</strong> and <strong>drained black beans</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up</p>",
