    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>smoked paprika</strong>, <strong>ground cumin</strong> and <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (Can't handle the heat? Go easy!) in a small bowl with 3 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[4 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[6 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and give it a good mix up – this is your <strong>spice mix</strong></p>",
